des:
Prolink mEzee provides users with a simple, convenient, easy to setup/paired with multiple Smart Home Devices. The app is designed to allow users to access, manage, as well as to preset automated scenarios; all from the convenience of your smartphone.
After connecting Alexa to your mEzee products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "mEzee" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register an account in our "mEzee" app;
(3). You need to have some mEzee devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our "mEzee" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "mEzee" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "mEzee" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "mEzee", and you'll be navigated to "mEzee" login page;
(9). Input your mEzee account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished.
You can enjoy the voice control on your smart home devices through voice commands such as:
“Alexa, turn on the bedroom light.”
“Alexa, turn off the bedroom light.”
“Alexa, turn on airconditoner.”
“Alexa, set the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa, brighten the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa, dim the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa, set bedroom light to green.”
“Alexa, set bedroom light to cool white.”
